# Project Description
Kuberan is a personal finance application aimed to allow users to efficiently manage their finances, make budgets, track their investments, and ultimately allow the user to make better financial decisions.

## General Requirements
- Users are able to sign in to their account.
- Users are able to create accounts, such as cash, investments, debts, etc.
- For cash accounts, users are able to key in daily transactions done.
- For investments, users are able to track their investment performance and their P/L (which requires entering their cost basis).
- Users should be able to access a dashboard (as their home page) to have an overview of their finances with informational graphs.
- Users should be able to plan budgets based on categories.
